						<summary>

						<p>This inscription records the gift of land for making offerings to the temple of Śivadha[r]mīśvaramuḍaiya mahādēva at Tirukkōḷakkuḍi in Puramaḷaināḍu, by Kaṇḍaṉ Sundaravalli <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Tuvarāpativēlaṉ of Kaṇṇamaṅgalam in Chōḻapāṇḍyavaḷanāḍu.</p>						

