<lb n="11"/>coḻapāṇṭiya vaḷaṉā<supplied reason="omitted">ṭ</supplied>ṭuk kiḻava
<lb n="12"/>kaiyil cempaṅkuṭi cū<supplied reason="omitted">ḻ</supplied>nta peru
